attributes.description: Specifies the media type of the <style> tag

SUMMARY.description: Defines a visible heading for a <details> element

attributes.name: align
attributes.description: Specifies the alignment of a table according to surrounding text

attributes.name: bgcolor
attributes.description: Specifies the background color for a table

attributes.name: border
attributes.description: Specifies whether or not the table is being used for layout purposes

attributes.name: cellpadding
attributes.description: Specifies the space between the cell wall and the cell content

attributes.name: cellspacing
attributes.description: Specifies the space between cells

attributes.name: frame
attributes.description: Specifies which parts of the outside borders that should be visible

attributes.name: rules
attributes.description: Specifies which parts of the inside borders that should be visible

attributes.name: sortable
attributes.description: Specifies that the table should be sortable

attributes.name: summary
attributes.description: Specifies a summary of the content of a table

attributes.name: width
attributes.description: Specifies the width of a table

TBODY.description: Groups the body content in a table

attributes.name: align
attributes.description: Aligns the content inside the <tbody> element

attributes.name: char
attributes.description: Aligns the content inside the <tbody> element to a character

attributes.name: charoff
attributes.description: Sets the number of characters the content inside the <tbody> element will be aligned from the character specified by the char attribute

attributes.name: valign
attributes.description: Vertical aligns the content inside the <tbody> element

TD.description: Defines a cell in a table

attributes.name: abbr
attributes.description: Specifies an abbreviated version of the content in a cell

attributes.name: align
attributes.description: Aligns the content in a cell

attributes.name: axis
attributes.description: Categorizes cells

attributes.name: bgcolor
attributes.description: Specifies the background color of a cell

attributes.name: char
attributes.description: Aligns the content in a cell to a character

attributes.name: charoff
attributes.description: Sets the number of characters the content will be aligned from the character specified by the char attribute

attributes.name: colspan
attributes.description: Specifies the number of columns a cell should span

attributes.name: headers
attributes.description: Specifies one or more header cells a cell is related to

attributes.name: height
attributes.description: Sets the height of a cell

attributes.name: nowrap
attributes.description: Specifies that the content inside a cell should not wrap

attributes.name: rowspan
attributes.description: Sets the number of rows a cell should span

attributes.name: scope
attributes.description: Defines a way to associate header cells and data cells in a table

attributes.name: valign
attributes.description: Vertical aligns the content in a cell

attributes.name: width
attributes.description: Specifies the width of a cell

TEXTAREA.description: Defines a multiline input control (text area)

attributes.name: autofocus
attributes.description: Specifies that a text area should automatically get focus when the page loads

attributes.name: cols
attributes.description: Specifies the visible width of a text area

attributes.name: dirname
attributes.description: Specifies that the text direction of the textarea will be submitted

attributes.name: disabled
attributes.description: Specifies that a text area should be disabled

attributes.name: form
attributes.description: Specifies one or more forms the text area belongs to

attributes.name: maxlength
attributes.description: Specifies the maximum number of characters allowed in the text area

attributes.name: name
attributes.description: Specifies a name for a text area

attributes.name: placeholder
attributes.description: Specifies a short hint that describes the expected value of a text area

attributes.name: readonly
attributes.description: Specifies that a text area should be read-only

attributes.name: required
attributes.description: Specifies that a text area is required/must be filled out

attributes.name: rows
attributes.description: Specifies the visible number of lines in a text area

attributes.name: wrap
attributes.description: Specifies how the text in a text area is to be wrapped when submitted in a form

TFOOT.description: Groups the footer content in a table

attributes.name: align
attributes.description: Aligns the content inside the <tfoot> element

attributes.name: char
attributes.description: Aligns the content inside the <tfoot> element to a character

attributes.name: charoff
attributes.description: Sets the number of characters the content inside the <tfoot> element will be aligned from the character specified by the char attribute

attributes.name: valign
attributes.description: Vertical aligns the content inside the <tfoot> element

TH.description: Defines a header cell in a table

attributes.name: abbr
attributes.description: Specifies an abbreviated version of the content in a header cell

attributes.name: align
attributes.description: Aligns the content in a header cell

attributes.name: axis
attributes.description: Categorizes header cells

attributes.name: bgcolor
attributes.description: Specifies the background color of a header cell

attributes.name: char
attributes.description: Aligns the content in a header cell to a character

attributes.name: charoff
attributes.description: Sets the number of characters the content will be aligned from the character specified by the char attribute

attributes.name: colspan
attributes.description: Specifies the number of columns a header cell should span

attributes.name: headers
attributes.description: Specifies one or more header cells a cell is related to

attributes.name: height
attributes.description: Sets the height of a header cell

attributes.name: nowrap
attributes.description: Specifies that the content inside a header cell should not wrap

attributes.name: rowspan
attributes.description: Specifies the number of rows a header cell should span

attributes.name: scope
attributes.description: Specifies whether a header cell is a header for a column, row, or group of columns or rows

attributes.name: sorted
attributes.description: Defines the sort direction of a column

attributes.name: valign
attributes.description: Vertical aligns the content in a header cell

attributes.name: width
attributes.description: Specifies the width of a header cell

THEAD.description: Groups the header content in a table

attributes.name: align
attributes.description: Aligns the content inside the <thead> element

attributes.name: char
attributes.description: Aligns the content inside the <thead> element to a character

attributes.name: charoff
attributes.description: Sets the number of characters the content inside the <thead> element will be aligned from the character specified by the char attribute

attributes.name: valign
attributes.description: Vertical aligns the content inside the <thead> element

attributes.name: datetime
attributes.description: Represent a machine-readable date/time of the <time> element

TITLE.description: Defines a title for the document

TR.description: Defines a row in a table

attributes.name: align
attributes.description: Aligns the content in a table row

attributes.name: bgcolor
attributes.description: Specifies a background color for a table row

attributes.name: char
attributes.description: Aligns the content in a table row to a character

attributes.name: charoff
attributes.description: Sets the number of characters the content will be aligned from the character specified by the char attribute

attributes.name: valign
attributes.description: Vertical aligns the content in a table row

TRACK.description: Defines text tracks for media elements (<video> and <audio>)

attributes.name: default
attributes.description: Specifies that the track is to be enabled if the user's preferences do not indicate that another track would be more appropriate

attributes.name: kind
attributes.description: Specifies the kind of text track

attributes.name: label
attributes.description: Specifies the title of the text track

attributes.name: src
attributes.description: Specifies the URL of the track file

attributes.name: srclang
attributes.description: Specifies the language of the track text data (required if kind="subtitles")

U.description: Defines text that should be stylistically different from normal text

attributes.name: compact
attributes.description: Specifies that the list should render smaller than normal

attributes.name: type
attributes.description: Specifies the kind of marker to use in the list

attributes.name: autoplay
attributes.description: Specifies that the video will start playing as soon as it is ready

attributes.name: controls
attributes.description: Specifies that video controls should be displayed (such as a play/pause button etc)

attributes.name: height
attributes.description: Sets the height of the video player

attributes.name: loop
attributes.description: Specifies that the video will start over again, every time it is finished

attributes.name: muted
attributes.description: Specifies that the audio output of the video should be muted

attributes.name: poster
attributes.description: Specifies an image to be shown while the video is downloading, or until the user hits the play button

attributes.name: preload
attributes.description: Specifies if and how the author thinks the video should be loaded when the page loads

attributes.name: src
attributes.description: Specifies the URL of the video file

attributes.name: width
attributes.description: Sets the width of the video player
